snippet.title: Johnny Depp Wins Court Battle Over Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Justice for Johnny is underway! Johnny Depp has finally won a court battle against Amber Heard. Depp now has access to the documents that show how much Heard donated to domestic violence victims. While a small step for Depp, it is a step in the right direction!
